[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "イ、イザナちゃん！　この人すっごい怪しいよ！\nついていっちゃダメな人だよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00071",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "うん。ハンマーも怪しいって言ってる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00072",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "でも、なんだか面白そうだから\n話だけでも聞いてみようよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00073",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "うーん……とりあえず話だけだよ！\n怪しかったら、すぐ逃げようね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00074",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "分かった！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00075",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "こんにちは！\nあの、お名前聞いてもいいですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00076",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "こんにちは。ええ、もちろんですわ。\n信頼関係を構築するために自己紹介は欠かせませんもの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00077",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "改めて、わたくしはララ・トロッケル。\nララ・プロダクションの社長をしていますわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00078",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "ららぷろだくしょん……？\nレスナちゃん、知ってる？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00079",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "聞いたことあるような……？\nちょっと調べてみよっか。えっと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00080",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "「芸能事務所。国民的歌手のディオーナや人気芸人の\n　ミーケを始め、数多くのスターが所属」……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00081",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "あーっ！　ディオーナにミーケ！　知ってるよ！\nえっ、そこの社長さんなの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00082",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ええ。知っていてくれたようで何よりですわ。\nあなたに声をかけたのも、その仕事関係でして",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00083",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "実は近々、アニマル系アイドルをコンセプトにした\nユニットをデビューさせたいと考えてますの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00084",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "アイドル……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00085",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "そのメンバーを探していた折、あなたを見かけて――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00086",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ビビッ！　……と、わたくしに電流が走ったのです。\n類稀なる社長の直感ですわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00087",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ユニットの他のメンバーはすでに揃っていて、\nデビューに向けたレッスンに励んでもらっていますわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00088",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "もし少しでも興味があれば、今からレッスン場へ行って\n見学してみませんこと？　雰囲気が掴めますわよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00089",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "イザナちゃん……どうする？\n本物の社長さんっぽいから、嘘じゃないと思うけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00090",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "うん……！　なんか面白そうだから見てみたい！\nレッスン、見学しに行こう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00091",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "あれ……？　あの、ララさん。\nこの先はランターナ学園ですが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00092",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ええ。冬休みの間、教室をレッスン場として\n貸し出してもらっていますの。ＯＧの特権ですわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00093",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "本当なら専用スタジオを用意したいのですが、\nアイドルをプロデュースするのは初めてですから……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00094",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "我がプロダクションのアイドル活動が軌道に乗ったら、\n専用のスタジオを建てる予定ですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00095",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "へぇ～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00096",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "さあ、教室へ行きましょう。\n未来のスターたちが待っていますわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00097",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ララ・トロッケル",
		"romanized_name": "Lara Trockel",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "芸能事務所「ララ・プロダクション」の社長。\nやり口は多少強引だが、才能を見抜く目は確か",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]